Tools to manipulate font files
FontTools/TTX is a library to manipulate font files from Python.
It supports reading and writing of TrueType/OpenType fonts,
reading and writing of AFM files, reading (and partially writing)
of PS Type 1 fonts. The package also contains a tool called "TTX"
which converts TrueType/OpenType fonts to and from an XML-based format.

